{"tid":2193443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拔苗基金：捐錢俾我啦，我致力保護兒童免受侵害（但不包括受：警察、行政會議成員、權貴、黨官、國企等一類）","createTime":"2020-09-08T00:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T05:43:05.000Z","uid":230104,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6954753b7bfbe1e222188c81f425f05d03629bb9","tid":2193443,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:43:48.000Z","msg":"籌款效益高，每HK$100捐款的成本為HK$8。雖然項目費用約佔總支出64%，未足七成，但2008至2009年度共接觸超過50,000名小學及中學生，和約1,400名智障兒童，教導他們如何避免性侵犯及自我保護#。平均$90善款就能向一名兒童提供避免性侵犯教育。另設有護苗線提供電話求助服務、輔導服務予侵犯者及受害人、圖書館供市民和專業人士查閱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n# 不包括"},{"pid":"7ac07d95f28146643aa3f293447a764f5e611928","tid":2193443,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"佢地唔講 如果一人一email 追問會點"},{"pid":"1b1644a4702d09b28184a3d572b2b078edd9168e","tid":2193443,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ac07d95f28146643aa3f293447a764f5e611928","tid":2193443,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:45:31.000Z","msg":"佢地唔講 如果一人一email 追問會點"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:46:50.000Z","msg":"需要群眾鍥而不捨既追問精神，切勿三分鐘熱度"},{"pid":"6239b2ab203b81cfd53fb38422d9cc7e2c6e6810","tid":2193443,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"林鄭讓我一次見清晒呢類偽善機構"},{"pid":"4ef93f180d8c3adeabd3b847b166aefd5b346ee3","tid":2193443,"uid":335434,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T00:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CV9KmGk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCV9KmGk.gif&h=c759c0cb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n保護兒童靠「護紅苗基金」不如靠湯家驊議員仲好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77818c46d72857f40c802632d71eb418a7707727","tid":2193443,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T01:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2j6z3o.jpg\" data-thumbnai